            <scopecontent id="aspace_28a9d193f61c69549161339cc3dfdc45">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This series includes illustrations, cartoons, and two oil paintings. Subjects include pastoral, domestic, humorous, sporting, political (notably two political cartoons on feminism), and several portraits. Of particular note are an original print from 1597 (Folder 4) and an erotic Western scene (Folder 5).</p>
            </scopecontent>
